              <span id="reviewTextContainer3294256060" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3996705055006253961">this is ... i honestly can&apos;t even put it into words how much i loved this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText3996705055006253961" style="display:none">this is ... i honestly can't even put it into words how much i loved this book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3996705055006253961" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

